title: Lazy Girl Full Body Fat Burn Workout | 10 Mins | No Jumping, Low Impact, At Home
description:
CALLING ALL LAZY/LOW ENERGY HUNNIES! 

Sometimes we barely have any energy to workout and that is totally okay! We need to listen to our bodies and either have a rest day, or do a workout that is more suited to our energy level. 

This can sometimes prompt you to do even more, and will help you get your energy up even more...who knows you may feel motivated to do another workout after you complete this one.

I just want to let you know that Im proud of you for even looking for a workout right now with your level of energy! I'm so proud of you and know that you are going to feel stronger and more confident tomorrow because you put the intentional effort in today!

Todays Workout:
1. Feet Slide  & Scissor Arms
2. Glute Bridge Forward March
3. Side Lying Knee Tap Extensions
4. Hamstring Curl & Press
5. Swimmers
6. Hip Tappers
7. Slow Leg Lifts
8. Windsheild Wipers
9. Scissor Kicks
10. Lying Star Legs
